title: Coast Guard pelican to return to downtown Pensacola 18 hours ago
content: Coast Guard pelican to return to downtown Pensacola    PENSACOLA, Fla. (WEAR) —    The Coast Guard pelican statue will soon return to downtown Pensacola.    The pelican was removed several months ago to undergo renovations.    The fiberglass structure was restored and it's sporting a new paint job.    The official unveiling is scheduled for Saturday night.
